00:19:11.570 --> 00:19:17.570
I wish to focus today on one of the
most iconic of medieval monuments,

00:19:17.570 --> 00:19:20.610
the Church of Zvart'nots'.

00:19:20.610 --> 00:19:26.460
The form of Zvart'nots' has
inspired, both medieval and modern.

00:19:26.460 --> 00:19:32.390 position:56%
Zvart'nots' can be purchased in
